snippet.title: Master System Longplay [084] Power Strike (FM)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by MadMatty

EU/US version of Aleste (Recorded by T-0815)

Apart from the title, this video also has FM sound. I rarely got the powerups in the order I wanted so it will look messy or unoptimal in places. Id have liked to have tried a fully leveled shield (4).

There is also no story presented which the Aleste games normally have. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
